Hi.

01:29.656 --> 01:30.656
Hello there.

01:30.657 --> 01:31.657
What is this?

01:31.658 --> 01:32.658
A party.

01:32.659 --> 01:34.159
Party? For what?

01:34.160 --> 01:35.661
Mr. Tate's death.

01:39.165 --> 01:40.666
It's kind of strange, isn't it?

01:40.667 --> 01:41.667
Well, I didn't say

01:41.668 --> 01:43.169
